reviewText: Actually grew up surfing these golden years. Fond memories and people are now long gone.

It's a pity that we can't get better image quality out of this shootings because the movie definitely deserves it! The audio sounds good as advertised and the video has 1 hour and 9 min of awesome moments! I'm glad I bought it! :-)
Is it only 12 minutes long?  That's what the run time shows.
Coming from that era and knowing many of the North Shore bruddas, it was a trip down memory lane. Really, really enjoyed it.
